# ============================================================================
# Project-Specific Notes
# ============================================================================
#
# IMPORTANT FOR NKREPO:
#
# 1. NEVER commit config.ini (contains MySQL passwords, API keys)
# 2. NEVER commit malware samples from data/samples/
# 3. NEVER commit uploaded files from web/vue/uploads/
# 4. NEVER commit trained ML models (too large, use model registry)
# 5. NEVER commit .env.*.local files (contain local configuration)
# 6. DO commit .example and template files
# 7. DO commit YARA rules (.yar files)
# 8. DO commit documentation (.md files)
# 9. DO commit setup scripts (.bat, .sh files)
#
# ============================================================================
